column1: z is elevation of HAT in AHD.
sigma_km is the standard deviation of the Gaussian kernel used to bump up the elevation of the HAT.
TPXO9 Value (MSL) is the value of the TPXO9 dataset at the location of the tide gauge. Not used just for reference.
offset is the is the difference between the MSL and AHD values at the tide gauge location.
